Basket Analysis Chart visualization to Power BI:

In basket analysis network chart the size of bubble depend on lift value:
the Basket Analysis Chart is a traditional Scatter chart.
There is one thing to be careful about: when a product has connections with multiple products, the number shown is the sum of the support for the various connections. This number is meaningless. Even if the number itself is meaningless, a bigger number means that the product has important Lift (relationships) with other products therefore the product deserves further analysis.
Basket Analysis map
you can watch the relation between lift and support in basket, If you hold mouse on bubble you can see the confidence as well as lift and support
this chart help you can now analyze your product salesfind cross-selling opportunities!
At the top of dashboard there is two filter you can select apply filter in the other chart to analyze specific basket in dashboard.
